  • Field Details

    • INSTANCES

      public static final List<ValueCodeGenerator.Delegate> INSTANCES
      A list of ValueCodeGenerator.Delegate implementations for the following common bean definition property value types.
      • ManagedList
      • ManagedSet
      • ManagedMap
      • LinkedHashMap
      • BeanReference
      • TypedStringValue
      • AutowiredPropertyMarker
      When combined with the delegates for common value types, this should be added first as they have special handling for list, set, and map.
